sentences: Karl Tomas Bergh Strømme (born 26 February 1976 in Bergen, Norway) is a Norwegian jazz trumpeter.
In 2004 he was the recipient of a scholarships from The Léonie Sonning Music Prize.
Within the band Peloton he has released two albums, Selected Recordings (2007) and The Early Years (2011).
